{"lemma":"شَدِيداتٌ","slug":"شَدِيداتٌ","root":"ش.د.د","root_slug":"ش-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-د-د","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَدِيد","root":"شدد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":56},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21917"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"violent, strong, intense, severe, hard, difficult, acute, extreme"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"vigorous, powerful"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"persevering, firm"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"avaricious"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"thick, tight"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"oppressive"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"plosive","examples":[{"text":"وَمِنَ ٱلْحُرُوفِ ٱلشَّدِيدُ، وَهُوَ ٱلَّذِي يَمْنَعُ ٱلصَّوْتَ أَنْ يَجْرِيَ فِيهِ، وَهُوَ ٱلْهَمْزَةُ وَٱلْقَافُ وَٱلْكَافُ وَٱلْجِيمُ وَٱلطَّاءُ وَٱلتَّاء وَٱلدَّالُ وَٱلْبَاءُ. وَذَلِكَ أَنَّكَ لَوْ قُلْتَ ”أَلْحَجْ“ ثُمَّ مَدَدْتَ صَوْتَكَ لَمْ يَجْرِ ذَلِكَ."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃa.diːd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21917","headword_ar":"شَدِيدٌ","root":"$d","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Possessing the quality of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~ap","text_ar":"شِدَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, L:) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a substance and to an attribute:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firm, compact,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong, powerful, forceful; vigorous, robust, sturdy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, L, Msb;) applied to a thing, (Msb,) and to a man; (A, Mgh, L;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydu AlquwaY","text_ar":"شَدِيدُ القُوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) pl., applied to men,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$id~aA='u","text_ar":"اَشِدَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [applied to things and men]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$idaAdN","text_ar":"شِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ududN","text_ar":"شُدُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, L,) which last preserves its original form [without idghám] because not resembling a verb: (L:) also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"courageous, brave, firm of heart:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K: *) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"niggardly, tenacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avaricious;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muta$ad~idN","text_ar":"مُتَشَدِّدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, A, L, K:) and [as is implied by the first explanation above, and shown by frequent usage,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehement, violent, intense, pressing, severe, strict, rigorous, tight, strait"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult, hard"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard to be borne, troublesome, distressing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distressful, afflictive, calamitous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adverse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, KL, PS, &c.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa $adiydN EalaY qawomihi","text_ar":"هُوَ شَدِيدٌ عَلَى قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rigorous, to his people"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydN EalaY ka*aA","text_ar":"شَدِيدٌ عَلَى كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Niggardly, tenacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avaricious, of such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"] Aboo-Dhu-eyb says, using"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiyd","text_ar":"شَدِيد"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aHiyH","text_ar":"شَحِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"quote","text":"HadaronaAhu biAlA^avowaAbi fiY qaEori huw~apK\n                      \n                     \n                        $adiydK EalaY maA Dum~a fiY All~aHodi juwluhaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We lowered him, with the"},{"kind":"text","text":"grave-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clothes, into the bottom of a cavity in the ground, the sides whereof were tenacious of what was comprised in the lateral hollow which was the place of the corpse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) And the words of the Kur [c. 8],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA_in~ahu liHub~i Alxayori la$adiydN","text_ar":"وَاـِنَّهُ لِحُبِّ الخَيْرِ لَشَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Zj, mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And verily, on account of the love of wealth, he is niggardly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avaricious."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydu AlEayoni","text_ar":"شَدِيدُ العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a man, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiyodapu jafoni","text_ar":"شَدِيْدَةُ جَفْنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEayoni","text_ar":"العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"metaphorically applied by a poet to a she-camel, mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whom sleep does not overcome."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~adiydu","text_ar":"الشَّدِيدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) because of his strength and hardiness. (TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiyd","text_ar":"شَدِيد"},{"kind":"text","text":"with a subst. or an inf. n. following it in the gen. case, the latter having the article"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to it, or being prefixed to another noun in the gen. case, supplies the place of an intensive epithet; as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydu Als~awaAdi","text_ar":"شَدِيدُ السَّوَادِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intensely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very, black;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydu","text_ar":"شَدِيدُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgaDabi","text_ar":"الغَضَبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vehemently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceedingly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very, angry;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misokN $adiydu Alr~aAy^iHapi","text_ar":"مِسْكٌ شَدِيدُ الرَّايِحَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strong-smelling musk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN $adiydu bayaADi AlEayoni","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ شَدِيدُ بَيَاضِ العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man intensely white in the eye."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHuruwfu Al$~adiydapu","text_ar":"الحُرُوفُ الشَّدِيدَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The strong letters"},{"kind":"text","text":"] are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"those letters which, in a state of quiescence, prevent the current of the voice in their utterance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j","text_ar":"ج"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"d","text_ar":"د"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"T","text_ar":"ط"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"q","text_ar":"ق"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k","text_ar":"ك"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the letters comprised in the words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajadota Tabaqaka","text_ar":"اَجَدْتَ طَبَقَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","Msb","Mgh","A","Sb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}